            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>富驊(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5465:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5465\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5465-TW</a>)16日10:08上漲3.75元，股價漲停報41.55元，委買1,000張、委賣345,000張，成交1,596張。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主要業務為電腦外殼及其零組件製造加工買賣業務。五金零件、金屬零件製造加工買賣及沖床加工。五金加工鍛造鑄造業務。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>富驊(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5465:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5465\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5465-TW</a>)近5日股價上漲10.36%，櫃買市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲3.34%，股價漲幅表現優於大盤。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><div class=\"dzbcd51\"></div><div class=\"m1aaic49\"></div><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+215 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+107 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：+108 張</li> <li>融資增減：+65 張</li> <li>融券增減：+3 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
