            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>新晶投控(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3713:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3713\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3713-TW</a>)近5分K跌速3.76%，16日10:09報21.25元，成交158張，今日跌幅為1.62％。（註：漲跌速為5分K的漲跌幅）</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>新晶投控(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3713:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3713\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3713-TW</a>)近5日股價上漲20.33%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><section><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：-8 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：-8 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：0 張</li> </ul></section><div class=\"dzbcd51\"></div><div class=\"m1aaic49\"></div></main>",
